---
title: Chicken Over Garlic Parmesan Spaghetti with Tuscan Roasted Tomatoes
description: Love chicken alfredo? Then you’ll adore this dreamy dish. It’s a sophisticated riff on the classic with tons more flavor infused into every bite. There’s Tuscan-spiced chicken, oven-roasted garlic and tomatoes, and al dente spaghetti all coated in a creamy, cheesy sauce. It’s one of those hearty, soul-warming dishes that’s sure to put a smile on any pasta-lover’s face.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/60dc72a95854557dcb6bd5aa-a82059d4.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/chicken-over-garlic-parmesan-spaghetti-60dc72a95854557dcb6bd5aa-96a7916d.pdf
course: main course
time required: 40 minutes
servings: 2
author: Michelle Doll Olson
